The assignment folder contains 3 sub folders:

1- Perceptron 
	it contains 7 matlab files
	i- loadMNISTImages.m
	ii- loadMNISTLabels.m
	iii- perceptron.m (the main file, you should run this file to run the code)
	iv- hardLimitFunc.m
	v- training.m
	vi- testing.m
	viii- evaluation.m
	
2- SVM
	it contains 5 matlab files
	i-SVMMain.m (You should run this file to run the code)
	ii- loadMNISTImages.m
	iii- loadMNISTLabels.m
	iv- trainSVM.m
	v- generateConfusionMatrix.m
	
3- Logistic Regression
	it contains 7 matlab files
	i- main.m (you should run this file to run the logistic regression code)
	ii- classifier.m
	iii- computeCost1.m
	iv- evaluation.m
	v- loadMNISTImages.m
	vi- loadMNISTLabels.m
	vii- sigmoid.m
	
	
